    "As before, the obtained range is divided into quantized steps, which are then fixed during the fine-tuning.",
    "At the inference time, the quantized steps are scaled to the integer values on [-2 q-1, 2 q-1 -1] range (where q is the number of bits), whereas the other parameters are adjusted accordingly.",
